{
  "name": "RPlog_Spencer_RP_Test",
  "title": "Spencer's Death Star Infiltration Test",
  "summary": "This is a roleplay qualification test in which the New Republic Intelligence agent Spencer is briefed to infiltrate the Death Star alongside veteran Chief Bazil McKenzie and steal its technical plans. Disguised as Imperial technicians, Bazil and Spencer talk their way past a stormtrooper checkpoint in the station's computer core using forged IDs and fabricated orders. As they move to tap the core, Spencer mutters aloud about wondering why he joined the rebellion, and despite Bazil's frantic attempts to cover the slip, the stormtrooper commander seizes on the words and orders his squad to open fire. Bazil is gunned down and falls into the core, and Spencer is killed defiantly. The grim epilogue declares the mission a failure that cost the New Republic dearly, with the Empire retaking the galaxy.",
